{"title": "Heart and Science: A Story of the Present Time", "description": "Heart and Science is one of Wilkie Collins' didactic novels. It is the story of young doctor Ovid Vere, who fights for his love against all resistance of his family and their immediate circle of acquaintances. The novel features a large inheritance, a secret engagement, and an evil stepmother, but what makes the novel truly remarkable is that Wilkie Collins, who was always very fond of animals, speaks out in this volume against animal cruelty in the sciences.  - Summary by Carolin", "duration": 52350, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "326", "name": "Wilkie Collins"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/heart_and_science_1611_librivox/heart_science_1611.jpg", "copyright_year": "1883", "genres": ["General Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Crln Yldz Ksr"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Crln Yldz Ksr"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Sonia"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "The Prefaces", "readers": [7879], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_and_science_1611_librivox/heartandscience_00_collins_64kb.mp3", "duration": 590}, {"section": 1, "title": "Chapter I", "readers": [7879], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_and_science_1611_librivox/heartandscience_01_collins_64kb.mp3", "duration": 180}, {"section": 2, "title": "Chapter II", "readers": [7879], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_and_science_1611_librivox/heartandscience_02_collins_64kb.mp3", "duration": 911}, {"section": 3, "title": "Chapter III", "readers": [7879], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_and_science_1611_librivox/heartandscience_03_collins_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1135}, {"section": 4, "title": "Chapter IV", "readers": [7879], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/heart_and_science_1611_librivox/heartandscience_04_collins_64kb.mp3", "duration": 315}, {"section"